description:
The Platinum Card is your ticket to the Bivreost web extension structure! The complete collection includes 100 branded cards. Here are some of the benefits for our holders:

- Exclusive design.
- System avatar for the web extension.
- Guaranteed access to 1 presale BI token giveaway.
- Distribution of unrealized BI token sale input.
- Binding and synchronization with Telegram contacts.

We draw the attention of our users to the fact that one user cannot have several cards.
name: PLATINUM
